[gd_resource type="StandardMaterial3D" format=3 uid="uid://cf3hgtf0lwmhp"]

; Polished metal-plate floor for the Anthropic Constitutional Vault showcase.
; Lower roughness than the worn plates so the arena's amber lights and emissive
; trim throw crisp SSR streaks across it — the reflective floor is half the
; reason the dark vault reads as "expensive". Triplanar so the plate pattern is
; unbroken across the 42m span without UV seams.

